    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find. It has been meticulously cared for and stored in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a flawless exterior with no scratches, dents, or chips. The interior is equally pristine, smelling like new with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a complete service history and every feature functioning exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives like it's brand new.",
